originalText.text:
Decades of searching for optimal health & well-being has led me to IKTI and working with Virginie. It has been a profound, transformational experience.
V is a highly skilled, gifted, knowledgeable facilitator, teacher, healer, and guide.
She has worked with me on my journey of personal growth by using AK and a holistic approach; teaching me how to really connect with my body in order to heal & resolve a long list of old behavior patterns, trauma & chronic pain. I thought I knew what healthcare & self-care was, yet I always felt there was something missing. I found it here at IKTI. This is healthcare & self-care on a whole other level. It’s healing & empowering. Advanced Kinesiology has helped me create a healthy, strong version of myself through the balancing of the many aspects of my body and mind.
Now I am leading a life without chronic pain, a life with greater awareness and deeper self-love.
I am very grateful.
- Mary Ann, New York

I have attended classes and received personal Kinesiology sessions at IKTI. I found the training experience very professional. I had planned to study Kinesiology for a long time but could not find a school that suited my needs until I found IKTI.
Virginie is a well of knowledge and an excellent teacher. I still have a few modules left to finish at IKTI and am looking forward to it.
I am sure this institute will continue to be a big part of my life both educationally and therapeutically.
